main_text:
Assalomu alaykum xurmatli mijoz!😊 yanada yaxshiroq xizmat ko’rsatishimizga yordam bering. So’rovnomada ishtirok eting va 1.000.000 so’mlik vaucher yutish imkoniyatini qo’lga kiriting!

Pastdagi tugmalar yordamida o'zingizka kerakli bo'limni tanlang
choose_chapter: 👇 Bo'limni tanlang! 😊 Bu bosqichdan keyin sizga savollar ketma-ketligi taqdim qilinadi
thanks: Ishtirokingiz uchun raxmat😊. G’oliblarni xar oyning oxirida “Random” programmasi orqali jonli efirda aniqlaymiz. Omad tilaymiz!✊🏻
sixth_question_err: Iltimos yoshingizni yozma va misolda ko'rsatilgan shakilda kiriting

eighth_question_err: Iltimos telefon raqamingizni to'g'ri shaklda yozib yuboring yoki pastdagi tugmacha yordamida jo'nating
second_question: Narxga 10 ballik shkalada nechchi baho berasiz?
third_question: Assortimentga 10 ballik shkalada nechchi baho berasiz?
fourht_question: Xizmat ko’rsatish sifatiga 10 ballik shkalada nechchi baho berasiz?
